{"tid":2263514,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府指籌備選舉需時半年以上　押後一年非不合理","createTime":"2020-10-30T03:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T06:39:19.000Z","uid":45910,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"69518a6022057c2d3342437ad9da3b8c6e0686db","tid":2263514,"uid":45910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:08:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=410983\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D410983&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KAESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=ec3cd1d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D410983&h=56808efb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=410983</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】立法會討論押後立法會選舉的小組委員會，舉行首次會議。<br />\n<br />\n緊急情況換屆選舉日期規例小組委員會舉行會議，多名民主派議員指，疫情已經放緩，批評政府應盡快恢復選舉，不應該等到明年9月5日，又批評將第六屆立法會任期延長一年並不符合基本法。<br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局代表指，籌備選舉需要至少半年，認為押後選舉一年是合理安排。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員（區議會第二） 鄺俊宇：「疫情放緩了，可以行街、食飯、行山、去博物館，好難說服香港市民為何現在不能投票。」<br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局副秘書長陳潔玲：「<span class=\"red\">換屆選舉準備最少要四個月，接著下來為公平起見，是否需要重啟選民登記活動，讓滿18歲選民可以登記，如是否的我們又要再花幾個月去做選民登記，所以整個籌備工夫要六個月或以上。</span>」"},{"pid":"c543cf6593e2919685e78fe37baa8ef842dc00f8","tid":2263514,"uid":45910,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:09:40.000Z","msg":"2020上半年成個政府無人開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n3月至9月份糧白逗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"7fc12b8853d0796a4d5c19e23a3e60729cdd43bd","tid":2263514,"uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:15:12.000Z","msg":"實際上係話你押後唔合理，唔關一年事"},{"pid":"ab7cbc2e5294bc9cfda02e7658ad3321234719a6","tid":2263514,"uid":45910,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T03:16:14.000Z","msg"